title: Commission Regulation (EEC) No 2207/91 of 23 July 1991 amending Regulation (EEC) No 2006/80 determining the intervention centres for cereals
header:
COMMISSION REGULATION (EEC) No 2207/91  of 23 July 1991  amending Regulation (EEC) No 2006/80 determining the intervention centres for cereals
THE COMMISSION OF THE EUROPEAN COMMUNITIES
main_body:
1. The sections headed 'FRANCE' and 'GREECE' in the Annex to Regulation (EEC) No 2006/80 are hereby replaced by Annexes I and II hereto.
2. The intervention centres 'Grimmen' and 'Neubuckow' (Land Mecklenburg - Western Pomerania) in the section headed 'FEDERAL REPUBLIC OF GERMANY' are hereby replaced by 'Stralsund' and 'Wismar' respectively.

This Regulation shall enter into force on the third day following its publication in the Official Journal of the European Communities.
It shall apply from 1 July 1991. This Regulation shall be binding in its entirety and directly applicable in all Member States.
